enhanced_by.reason: Both methods perform input validation to ensure non-null parameters.
Both methods involve the initialization of an UnmodifiableOrderedMapIterator object.
The unmodifiable iterator's getKey() method returns the same key as the decorated iterator.
The unmodifiable iterator's getValue() method returns the same value as the decorated iterator.
The unmodifiable iterator's hasNext() method returns the same result as the decorated iterator.
The unmodifiable iterator's hasPrevious() method returns the same result as the decorated iterator.
The unmodifiable iterator's next() method returns the same result as the decorated iterator.
The unmodifiable iterator's previous() method returns the same result as the decorated iterator.
